<h3>How to make references to this website ?</h3>
<p>All the items description page (agglomeration, treatment plant, discharge point and sensitive areas) can be accessed directly, and then referenced on other websites.</p>
<p>This can be done by using the following URL pattern: http://uwwtd.oieau.fr/Croatia/[year]/[name of the element]/[ID of the element];<br />For instance:</p>
<ul>
   <li>http://uwwtd.oieau.fr/croatia/agglomeration/hrag_0001116/2012</li>
   <li>http://uwwtd.oieau.fr/croatia/treatment-plant/hruwwtp_0001116_001/2012</li>
   <li>http://uwwtd.oieau.fr/croatia/discharge-point/hrdp_0001116_001/2012</li>
</ul>
